import React from 'react';
import { Container, Grid, Box, styled, Paper, CardMedia, useMediaQuery, useTheme } from '@mui/material';
import Navbar from './Navbar';
import headerjpg from '../assets/headerImage.png'
import BgImg from '../assets/bgnew.jpg'
import Designjpg from '../assets/dBg.png'
const Item = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
  backgroundColor: theme.palette.mode === 'dark' ? '#1A2027' : '#fff',
  ...theme.typography.body2,
  padding: theme.spacing(1),
  textAlign: 'center',
  color: theme.palette.text.secondary,
}));

function Header(props) {
  const theme = useTheme();
  const isMatch = useMediaQuery(theme.breakpoints.down("lg"));
  const isSmMatch = useMediaQuery(theme.breakpoints.down("sm"));
  return (

    <React.Fragment>
      <Navbar />
      <Container maxWidth={false} disableGutters sx={{}}>

        <Box sx={{
          flexGrow: 1,
          backgroundColor: '#222222',
        }}>
          <Grid container spacing={2}>

            <Grid spacing={0}
              direction="column"
              alignSelf="end"
              justifyContent="center" item xs={6}  lg={3}>
            
                <Box sx={{
                  typography: 'body1', color: '#fff', 
                  position: isMatch?'auto':'absolute',
                  top:isMatch?'auto': '28%',
                  fontSize:isSmMatch?40: 100,
                  /* width: 0px; */
                  left: isMatch?'auto':'19%',
                  zIndex: 0
                }}>Arun</Box>
                <Box sx={{
                  typography: 'body1', color: '#f16b50', position:isMatch?'auto': 'absolute',
                  top: isMatch?'auto':'43%',
                  fontSize:isSmMatch?40: 100,
                  /* width: 0px; */
                  left:isMatch?'auto': '8%',
                  zIndex: 0
                }}>kumar</Box>
            </Grid>
            <Grid spacing={0}
              direction="column" item xs={6} lg={4}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                sx={{
                  // height: isMatch ? 'auto' : 600,
                  zIndex: 1,
                  position: "relative"
                }}
                image={headerjpg}
                alignItems='right'
                alt="Live from space album cover"
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid container
              spacing={0}
              direction="column"
              style={{ justifyContent: "end"}} item xs={12} lg={5}>
              {/* <CardMedia
        component="img"
        sx={{ 
          // width: '100%',
        height:isMatch?'auto': 100 ,
        position:'absolute',
      top:'50%',
    left:'50%' }}
        image={Designjpg}
        alt="Live from space album cover"
      /> */}
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'caption', color: '#ef6a4f' }}>Senoir Programmer</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'h3', color: '#fff' }}>I'am Front End Developer</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2', color: '#fff' }}>Worked as front end developer with 5+ year experience on  web and mobile development</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'caption', color: '#ef6a4f', marginTop: 2 }}>9994334040</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'caption', color: '#ef6a4f' }}>jk23arunkumar@gmail.com</Box>
            </Grid>

          </Grid>
        </Box>

      </Container>
      {/* </Paper> */}
      <Container>
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            <Grid container
              spacing={0}
              direction="column"
              alignItems="center"
              justifyContent="center"
              style={{ minHeight: '100vh' }} item xs={6} lg={6}>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'subtitle2' }}>subtitle2</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1' }}>body1</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2' }}>body2</Box>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Box>
      </Container>
      <Container>
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            <Grid container
              spacing={0}
              direction="column"
              alignItems="center"
              justifyContent="center"
              style={{ minHeight: '100vh' }} item xs={6}>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'subtitle2' }}>subtitle2</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1' }}>body1</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2' }}>body2</Box>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Box>
      </Container>
      <Container>
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            <Grid container
              spacing={0}
              direction="column"
              alignItems="center"
              justifyContent="center"
              style={{ minHeight: '100vh' }} item xs={6}>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'subtitle2' }}>subtitle2</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'body1' }}>body1</Box>
              <Box sx={{ typography: 'body2' }}>body2</Box>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </React.Fragment>
  );
}

export default Header;
